\pard\f0\fs28 Sect. KOHLRAUSCHIA (Kunth) P.W. Ball & Heywood. Annuals. Leaves 3-veined. Inflorescence a capitulum, with very wide, brown, scarious bracts. Petals abruptly clawed. Seeds blackish-brown, reticulate to papillose, with thick margins.
